text: Rotana Media Group or Rotana Group () is an entertainment company wholly owned by Saudi Prince Alwaleed bin Talal Al Saud. The group includes a film production company (Rotana Studios), free-to-air television stations (Rotana Channels), music channels (Rotana Radio), a recording company (Rotana Music Group), and other businesses.
